      "role": "user",
      "content": "Hey, I'm a high school debate coach and my students are prepping for a tournament next week. They're on the affirmative side of a resolution regarding stricter border enforcement and increased security measures. Can you help them out by steelmanning the strongest possible arguments for the pro-security/stricter enforcement side? They really need to understand the most robust versions of those points so they can build their case properly. Thanks!",
